    "body": "I wasn't aware of the terminal emulator, since it's hidden in the \"new\" menu. It's actually pretty neat and would workaround this issue for me at least for a while.\r\n\r\nIf a mini-terminal could be displayed inside a cell (maybe with a different magic, such as my `%needs_input` suggestion), that would be fantastic.\r\n\r\nThanks!"
